KeysToEntries.story_2_2_000:
No way…
Me? Twice?
Here of all places…
KeysToEntries.story_2_2_002:
Keep this up…
and you’ll lose next time too‼
KeysToEntries.story_2_2_004:
And you there…
You’ve got skill, but
you’re still soft…
KeysToEntries.story_2_2_005_1:
Get sharper first…
then return here.
KeysToEntries.story_2_2_005_2:
Next time,
I’ll face you myself.
